➜一组英文漫画反应教育的真正目的
http://www.sohu.com/a/424578137_100171577	23329
<p class="ql-align-justify">美国杜克大学用14幅漫画，向毕业生讲述了学校对其未来的期许。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这也是真正受教育者终其一生应该具备的思维方式。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Living A Good LIfe.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「01」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>坚持</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Stick with it</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201014/3eccd0e04b604503aad8e3f768692d1f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你想最大化自己的潜能，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坚持在专注的领域不断精深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「02」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回报社会</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Give back</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201014/8b67017cab7e4355a498704643b577a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">一颗感恩的心回报他人，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一颗慷概的心给予他人，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二者同样重要。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「03」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>做自己，善于学习</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Be true to yourself</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201014/10e3e5e767f84520825796b5d9c3aa93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接受教育不仅是获得知识，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">学会学习，才能自我升级。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「04」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灵感来自阅读</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Reading leads to inspiration</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201014/215db823bbd2485499430a824b90aa77.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阅读激发灵感，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实践带来提升。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「05」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>善意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Be kind</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仁慈的对待他人，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让善意像空气一样流动。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「06」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>聪明不代表受教育</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Educated ≠ Smart</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201014/341c11169b7243649819761b55c99dc2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">教育让你既独立思考，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又能善于倾听，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时后者更加重要。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「07」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>教育让你学会反思</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Stop and look back</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201014/d5a12645cb424bcb972dc8d555c13cb2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">请允许自己时不时停下脚步，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回望过去，并思考它的意义。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「08」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拥抱不确定的生活</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Embrace ambiguity</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201014/d2afa0ff58d74d7a8867d26b1f84dbc1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生命的本质就是不确定，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勇敢接受，自有乐趣。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「09」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>价值在挑战中实现</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">This is your Life</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">个人价值与经历的挑战正相关，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们总是爱停留在舒适区，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但停止脚步，也意味着甘于平庸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「10」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>学会在拒绝中找机遇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Reframe rejection</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201014/cdceade07c904c6f8333400bab64b613.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拒绝不是终结，而是给你机会，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去学会等待和进行再一次尝试。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「11」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>关注人本身，而非头衔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Respect people over job titles</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201014/cbc93a191dab427ba9192921852593ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你永远不知道你会在别人身上学到什么，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保持谦虚，向他人学习的习惯绝不会错。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「12」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“关系”比“物质”重要</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Relationships matter</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201014/055a9f7c2cea4fad90b9032b44627ad1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从与人们建立友好关系中获得满足感，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">物质的占有其实没有想象的那么幸福。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「13」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人生选择没有对错</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">No right or wrong</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201014/759aa0251d6e4759bdee6a594221f7ab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与其让迷茫和焦虑占领自己的内心，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不如冷静的部署，执着的坚持，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然而然，未来就在看得见的远方。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「14」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>别过无意识的生活</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Pay close Attention</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201014/eaf3b3dcc8b74f7382742d3d6f3664ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别让生活悄然熘走而浑然不觉，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别在周而复始中遗忘了为何出发，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">留心观察，用心体会。</p>